    • scanNumber

      private Token scanNumber()
      Scan a unsigned number. 
       Reference-Syntax:
     unsigned-number
       = decimal-number  [  exponent-part  ]
       | exponent-part
     decimal-number
       = unsigned-integer  [  decimal-fraction  ]
       | decimal-fraction
     decimal-fraction
       = .  unsigned-integer
     exponent-part
       =  ( invalid input: '&' | invalid input: '&'invalid input: '&' )  [ + | - ]  unsigned-integer
     unsigned-integer
       =  digit  {  digit  |  _  }
       |  radix  R  radix-digit  {  radix-digit  |  _  radix-digit  }
     radix
       =  2  |  4  |  8  |  16
     radix-digit
       =  digit  |  A  |  B  |  C  |  D  |  E  |  F
      End-Condition:
      • current is last character of construct
      • getNext will return first character after construct
      Returns:
      A Item representing a constant number.
